ebdf6a5f4663000df51c0 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230219-mayron-pe-2-walking-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=1d075372cf66c8d11aa2711626746470 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230219-mayron-pe-2-walking-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=6d7536075ff2e90bdbd985cc175e96a2 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230219-mayron-pe-2-walking-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1428&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=87dcd5bff476efdf98cdfc2ad8f1acbd 2000w"></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only" data-step-fx-show="10" style=""></div></div></section><section class="section-chapter-3"><div class="scrolly"><div class="custom-chapter-break | scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="cb3" data-step-fx-before-bg="3" data-step-fx-after-bg="4"></div><div class=""><div class="scrolly__step"><p class="fade--text text-style-copy--lg">Mayron was at work in June when she got a call from the babysitter. Sheriff’s deputies had arrived at the door with an arrest warrant.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only" data-step-fx-show="11" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step"><div class="stack stack--row stack--spacing-gutter stack--align-start stack--collapse-below-lg"><div class="sticky-element | stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size06 left out03 wide-md"><p>Mayron thought the case related to leaving Zooey in the car was still working its way through the courts. She didn’t understand why she was being arrested again.</p><p>She was afraid things would escalate and drag her back into a costly legal battle. A conviction — or worse, a prison sentence — could mean losing the girls. Just fighting it could push them further into debt.</p><p>That afternoon, she stopped at a bar for a drink. Alcohol was never her drug of choice, she said. She told herself she could handle a few drinks while she figured out her next step.</p></div><div class="stack stack--col stack__item-no-shrink | stack--spacing1 | size05 right out02 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="2142" height="3000" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=0ebdada769dc47f6b7588bd2ae3fbeb2" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=560&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=6fbfc56a402450dbed8c726a681a5f41 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=0ebdada769dc47f6b7588bd2ae3fbeb2 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1681&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=ce461bd07923c8c71badb97cd40e9035 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1821&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=0b8f580fce63eccd61902604363ae494 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2031&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=6709324c2bbba97ecffaf3120821e349 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2241&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=484ef45ffc7d6b6cf96500425e2481ae 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-court-corner-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2801&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=6e32048b71802c3ffdaf654aa9a09676 2000w"> <img class="" alt="" width="2142" height="3000" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=2543014ca33af5dbbade26e8c70fcf95" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=560&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=d8f595b32fb5ac14d437273ec6eb4572 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=2543014ca33af5dbbade26e8c70fcf95 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1681&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=2303ea2b9d9aa71c4fddcf6c6492da36 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1821&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=6b288a932f21bcbd203f54db06550467 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2031&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=8ffd00a68c0f659233bd3b2faf838dea 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2241&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=f906c53bc35c338b01aad7c6a9f284b1 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230624-mayron-pe-3-bar-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2801&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=962aad90fc5723864b0fdad7c3a392fc 2000w"></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="12" style=""></div><div class="size06 left out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="12"><p class="caption-bg">After speaking to a lawyer, Mayron prepared to turn herself in, kissing her babies goodbye.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--200"><div class="stack stack--row stack--spacing-gutter stack--align-start stack--collapse-below-lg"><div class="sticky-element | stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size06 left out03 wide-md"><p>She was told the arrest was necessary because the district attorney’s office had downgraded her charges to a misdemeanor. Sheriff’s deputies booked her into jail and quickly released her.</p><p>Mayron returned home to a sick baby: Elayna had another fever, so Mayron put her on the oxygen machine and waited for the doctor to call her back.</p></div><div class="stack stack--col stack__item-no-shrink | stack--spacing1 | size07 right out03 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-jail-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=1f92b358ac642336267d95f6b91173c8" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-jail-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=4c9f04f7f96cfe080f25d189a8064f4f 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-jail-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q