7&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=8459c376b5618a09e1f77a351c74d49b 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-worried-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=928&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=36b3e10e3d072348eb67dcdc6fe173cc 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-worried-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=617e2ca10329b1b395a54c7554f6a307 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-worried-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=183b31351c723fcbbb35eab90b7cd1b4 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230626-mayron-pe-3-worried-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1428&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=d7b1933871102532aafc4e18ff742e75 2000w"></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=e85933a62bc2ec09bc6415924704eb45" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=438e69bae9e2f2f86fa532497b684ae7 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=e85933a62bc2ec09bc6415924704eb45 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=857&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=29c978febdeef00f7213d04ff8bf90a0 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=928&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=182bc0e3143e18cebbbd37d25446997d 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=49a3dd880a06932f5aa4068ff4465658 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=9adf33963754b239f0a5932c588a11af 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20230705-mayron-pe-3-court-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1428&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=3a8e2736d66e77b295045eb4f467f743 2000w"><p>When she returned to court a month later, Mayron’s lawyer had negotiated a deal. To stay out of jail, Mayron pleaded guilty to reckless endangerment in exchange for one year of probation.</p></div><div class="size08 center"><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--75"><p>The outcome provided little comfort. Mayron knew any involvement with the criminal justice system could make it harder to provide for her family — she might need to miss work for probation check-ins and drug tests — and easier for her kids to get taken from her again if she made any more mistakes.</p><p>She worried what authorities would think about delta-8, the legal cannabinoid she used to calm her nerves.</p><p>To avoid it, she feared she’d end up turning more to alcohol.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only hide-on-desktop" style="margin-top:-100vh"></div><div class="scrolly__step"><div class="size10 center"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=dff3857bc3c6292df721b56b51166919" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=0062d0060b6479b48aa252dd62620401 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=dff3857bc3c6292df721b56b51166919 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=857&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=e25171247a4015a70cd726f7cf0fa534 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=928&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=085d4d7c157aee01ba0c8594d64b8892 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=3ebdec8527092a9abf1b2b5644c24841 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=9c59e9d41c629d5453c82d0ec6bffd69 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-vape-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1428&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=47ce6347d00745a416479132d6051feb 2000w"></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only hide-on-desktop" style="margin-top:-100vh"></div><div class="size08 center"><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--75"><p class="fade--text text-style-copy--lg">Then, summer brought more people to care for.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="13" style=""></div><div class="size06 right out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="13"><p class="caption-bg">After losing her housing in August, Mayron’s mother moved into the cramped two-bedroom house.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="13" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--150"><div class="stack stack--row stack--spacing-gutter stack--align-start stack--collapse-below-lg stack--column-reverse-below-lg"><div class="sticky-element | stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size06 left out03 wide-md"><p>Mayron’s mother shared a drafty second-floor room with Mayron’s father, her ex-husband, who also stayed with them.</p><p>Health issues kept Mayron’s mother mostly bed-bound. Her father often spent his nights drinking with the neighbors.</p><p>Tension led to fights.</p></div><div class="stack stack--col stack__item-no-shrink | stack--spacing1 | size07 right out03 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-mom-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=21d773003717e610c84e54a5828c1e7e" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-mom-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=615c09e5d28b161e262334ed202b510e 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-mom-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=21d773003717e610c84e54a5828c1e7e 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/202309-mayron-pe-3-mom-FINAL.JPG?crop=fo