p;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1681&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=bf37a798f4ad8ba402461abf74ecd5f6 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-neighbor-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1821&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=cb91df2ee5e6b49b90138e7b2d87db26 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-neighbor-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2031&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=5e89d40bf42a636c2edd93a0cf0ba68d 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-neighbor-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2241&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=498577420a5746b967d1d30ed82d3528 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-neighbor-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2801&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=8caaa4b088a09bc8f5c378d3554e7737 2000w"></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only hide-on-desktop" style="margin-top:-100vh"></div><div class=""><div class="scrolly__step"><p>When Chris came home the next week, he could see Mayron was unraveling.</p><p>The volatility reminded him of the times before they got serious about their recovery four years ago.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only" data-step-fx-show="20" style=""></div><div class=""><div class="scrolly__step"><p>The family was supposed to go to church the next morning, but Mayron disappeared that night and no one knew where she was.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="21" style=""></div><div class="size06 right out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="21"><p class="caption-bg">Chris took the girls anyway and tried to find a moment of peace as a family amid the chaos.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step"><div class="stack stack--row stack--spacing-gutter stack--align-center stack--collapse-below-lg"><div class="stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size06 left out03 wide-md"><p>Mayron came home with a black eye. She couldn’t remember how she got it.</p></div><div class="stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size05 right out02 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="2142" height="3000" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=fbeb62d3326bd08825730a5db32b4187" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=560&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=ad14f57a69ad92c0880d9b9d3af2d5b1 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1120&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=fbeb62d3326bd08825730a5db32b4187 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1681&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=06d9462b9e24c3caf7b4033301c524b4 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1821&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=b3909b3489ffe2a7c3a5e2e93a257aed 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2031&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=a1d3f3dccb0c379cc81e090dbb9d7ef9 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2241&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=712769575a7f7f41d4e9a595248b1384 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-black-eye-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=2801&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=74b4bcb3159918a22ee0094e37174bd0 2000w"></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only hide-on-desktop" style="margin-top:-75vh"></div><div class="size10 center"><div class="scrolly__step"><div class="fade--text"><p class="text-style-copy--lg">On Elayna’s first birthday, Dec. 13, Mayron and Chris fought all morning.</p></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="22" style=""></div><div class="size06 left out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="22"><div class="caption-bg"><p>Mayron wanted Chris to go to work, since the family debt had grown while he missed jobs and was getting treatment.</p></div></div></div><div class="size06 left out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="22"><div class="caption-bg"><p>He didn’t want to leave her alone with the kids in her current state.</p></div></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class=""><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--75"><p>Chris took the kids to the babysitter’s house.</p><p>That triggered her memories of other children who had been removed from her custody, years earlier.</p><p>Mayron exploded at him in the front yard.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" data-step-fx-show="23" style=""></div><div class="size06 left out03 wide-md"><div class="scrolly__step" data-step-fx-show="23"><p class="caption-bg">Neighbors showed deputies a video of Mayron hitting Chris. She was arrested.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only" data-step-fx-show="24" style=""></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only scrolly__step--50" style=""></div><div class="size08 center"><div class="scrolly__step"><p>Chris knew Mayron had been planning to do something special to mark Elayna’s first year. She had already bought a tablecloth, sparklers and some toys from the dollar store.</p><p>Despite the turmoil of the year, it felt significant to recognize her daughter had come a long way:</p><p>From less than 2 pounds, hooked up to breathing machines, to a curious infant, cuddling with her older sister and trying to figure out how to walk.</p></div></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--fx-only hide-on-desktop" style="margin-top:-75vh"></div><div class="scrolly__step scrolly__step--75"><div class="size10 center" style="margin-bottom: 1rem;"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=a98b7bb43d27a5d10f36c16b2d905896" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=4808e522dcb90b77a6c01b69faadf07d 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=a98b7bb43d27a5d10f36c16b2d905896 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=857&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=675b6c72af852b507469bf998769c038 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=928&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=e17b7b0ab6ec670b782acd1332f1de43 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=8b79dfe9fcea26e0525d0a9e8c0e9163 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=020e6de0580ced4278b5637661f52ba0 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231212-mayron-pe-4-elayna-alone-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1428&amp;q=75&amp;w=2000&amp;s=06e4f15d8ed8afdaa207ad5c5dd0dffb 2000w"></div></div><div class="scrolly__step"><div class="stack stack--row stack--spacing-gutter stack--align-center stack--collapse-below-lg"><div class="stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size06 left out03 wide-md"><p>With Mayron in jail, the celebration fell to Chris. As the sun began to set, he cleaned the living room and kitchen, then went to Big Lots and chose gifts: a Stack and Play Rainbow Cloud and a Fisher-Price toy telephone.</p><p>He picked up his daughters from the babysitter’s house, then took them to Publix to get dinner: hot dogs, mac and cheese, french fries, two cakes — one with Elayna’s name on it and one to smash — and a “Happy Birthday” balloon.</p></div><div class="stack__item-no-shrink | stack stack--col stack--spacing1 | size07 right out03 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-chris-girls-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=5942aa8db9c4ab668fd8c216214ad8f5" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images