t. He never found it.</p></div><div class="stack stack--col stack__item-no-shrink | stack--spacing1 | size07 right out03 wide-md"><img class="" alt="" width="3000" height="2142" loading="lazy" js-autosizes src="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=94e88b2fc0bb6d14b49cbb89a1674bb1" srcset="https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=286&amp;q=75&amp;w=400&amp;s=7df9566cbefc392c8744bac84731542d 400w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=571&amp;q=75&amp;w=800&amp;s=94e88b2fc0bb6d14b49cbb89a1674bb1 800w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=857&amp;q=75&amp;w=1200&amp;s=f89f282e96cf72acc8474cd9703c41b1 1200w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=928&amp;q=75&amp;w=1300&amp;s=ee6fb5e23e30ad592cdfd88e5ec329c2 1300w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1035&amp;q=75&amp;w=1450&amp;s=903daed4cc55b85d742b052a1c74d3ca 1450w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-y=0.5&amp;h=1142&amp;q=75&amp;w=1600&amp;s=d076b109c62589e49ce7cd5aae1f9ddd 1600w, https://img.assets-d.propublica.org/v5/images/20231213-mayron-pe-4-kids-balloons-FINAL.JPG?crop=focalpoint&amp;fit=crop&amp;fm=webp&amp;fp-x=0.5&amp;fp-